  <brief_title>Near Normalisation of BG Improves the Potentiating Effect of GLP-1</brief_title>
  <official_title>Near Normalisation of Blood Glucose Improves the Potentiating Effect of GLP-1 on Glucose Induced Insulin Secretion in Patients With Type 2 Diabetes</official_title>
  <sponsors>
