  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The ability of glucagon-like peptide 1 to enhance beta-cell responsiveness to I.v. glucose is
      impaired in patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus compared with healthy individuals. We
      investigated whether 4 weeks of near-normalisation og blood glucose improves the potentiation
      of glucose-stimulated insulin secretion by GLP-1
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
